Got it! I've added the following to your schedule:

* Every Tuesday and Thursday, 7 pm - 10 pm: Rehearsals at the local community theater
* Every Saturday morning: Dance classes at the dance studio near your house
* Every other Wednesday: Costume fittings at the theater's costume department

Let me ask, do you know the specific dates for the costume fittings, or would you like me to block out every other Wednesday for now and we can fill in the exact dates later?

Also, are there any other commitments or events you'd like to add to your schedule, or is that it for now?
